text.section:
The articles of organization shall set forth:
A name for the limited liability company that satisfies the requirements of KRS 14A.3-010;
The registered office and initial registered agent that satisfy the requirements of KRS 14A.4-010;
The mailing address of the initial principal office of the limited liability company; and
A statement that the limited liability company is to be managed by a manager or managers or that the limited liability company is to be managed by its members.
